      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Construction of offsite dam in Akatsi-Torve completed.</narrative>
      </comment>
     </target>
     <actual>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. The construction of a 200m offsite dam in Akatsi-Torve was completed. The dam will improve availability of water for agricultural and domestic use, in particular during the dry season, for about 5,000 low-income residents. At the same time, the excess runoff during the rainy season will be stored to prevent flooding of Torve and the surrounding villages (Agortoy, Dawlo, Yaluvi, and Nugblebi) downstream of the Tordzi River.</narrative>
